            <ed>Bha e a’ snàmh ??</ed></li>
          <li>Bha i a’ gnogadh air an doras <m>gu seachd uairean</m>. <en>She knocked on the door
              until seven o’clock.</en>
            <ed>Ghnog i air ... Ghnogadh i air ... ??</ed></li>
          <li>Bheireadh e flùraichean thuice gach madainn <m>gus a’ bhanais</m>. <en>He brought her
